    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/da05711ae52c9dbd9f11242ce79765eb.apng?t=1730265925\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/da05711ae52c9dbd9f11242ce79765eb.poster.avif?t=1730265925\" class=\"bb_img\" width=608 height=288 /></picture></span><br>Party on Hallow Grove is a small, cute <strong>halloween adventure game</strong> where you are tasked with throwing Death the best surprise birthday party <strong>EVER</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/5c8e2eebe668550ad05dc945c04bcf0c.poster.avif?t=1730265925\" width=528 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/5c8e2eebe668550ad05dc945c04bcf0c.webm?t=1730265925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/75aced6e23f96ecfa5dc27bebf4907b2.poster.avif?t=1730265925\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/75aced6e23f96ecfa5dc27bebf4907b2.webm?t=1730265925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/75aced6e23f96ecfa5dc27bebf4907b2.mp4?t=1730265925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You and Death go way back. You’ve been invited to his birthday party - and its gonna be a <i>big one</i>. But when you get there, nothing’s ready, and all of Death’s friends are being <strong>a**holes</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/61f6cd717156f88db5d5b2e81f50cf5b.poster.avif?t=1730265925\" width=528 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/61f6cd717156f88db5d5b2e81f50cf5b.webm?t=1730265925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/8f79bc16c69512e61009abb9ecf657ec.poster.avif?t=1730265925\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/8f79bc16c69512e61009abb9ecf657ec.webm?t=1730265925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/8f79bc16c69512e61009abb9ecf657ec.mp4?t=1730265925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>PoHG</i> is a <strong>top-down rpg</strong> with an emphasis on story, exploration, interaction, dialogue and item trading. Talk to kooky guests, explore the mansion, trade party items, put up decorations, and play some party music - all before Death wakes up from his death nap.<br><br>On your quest, you will laugh, make weird friends, and learn to be kind to one another - and when the party is crashed by an unexpected guest, you’ll be faced with your biggest challenge yet.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/f1e556c35e645d6c88c2ef655e45bbae.poster.avif?t=1730265925\" width=456 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096140/extras/f1e556c35e645d6c88c2ef655e45bbae.webm?t=1730265925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
